    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH predictions are within 12% of experimental values across all 5 operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion relative to the predicate device.",
